attributes.text: Extract the "Plugin Icon" symbol to `../assets/icon.png` so that it gets bundled and used in your plugin.
If you are using a GitHub repository for your plugin, you can use the "repo card" to generate a social card for it.
It is not recommended to track this Sketch file with Git as it can create conflicts without an additional version control tool.

value.text:
Instructions  ⚫︎ Extract the "Plugin Icon" symbol to `../assets/icon.png` so that it gets bundled and used in your plugin.
⚫︎ If you are using a GitHub repository for your plugin, you can use the "repo card" to generate a social card for it.

It is not recommended to track this Sketch file with Git as it can create conflicts without an additional version control tool.
